{
  "stem": "20684.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Sometimes they would throw us out and sometimes we'd get away with it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we would sit next to other children with empty seats and we'd get away with it like we're part of the family and we sort of-- and I remember one of the tricks that we used to have, one of his tricks, but I've learned my lesson.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I used to duck quickly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I learn quickly, I'm a good learner.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm not always clever, but a good leaner.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We used to go to Paris and we used to follow these good-looking mademoiselles that walked with a-- they used to walk with a wiggle in France, the ladies.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now it's not fashionable, but it was-- do you know how they used to wiggle in the '40s?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If you've seen in some of the films?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Yeah, you have?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they wiggled like that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one day, those wiggling ladies, we used to follow them-- Michel and I used to follow them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he-- he would place me in front of him and I would just walk.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we'd walk along the Champs Elysee in Paris, walking around behind these elegant ladies and pretending to be wiggling like that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And people would laugh.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one of them turned around and gave me such a whack.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was all his fault, you see.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So next time we'd wiggle around and when they turned around, I stood back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that was that-- and then run away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we used to play another sort of stupid game.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Another thing-- another one of his favorite games was it worked-- always worked, every time it worked when we're in Paris.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
